node.text: DAD HATS! Adorn your northernmost physical geography with the finest in scripted logos. You can snag one via moderntimesmerch.com (kitten not included).

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Modern Times Beer on July 30, 2021. May be an image of food and indoor.

node.text: BIG RIG, BABY. Ron's Little Big Rig is straight up stacked; chicken fried seitan, a pepper crusted patty, cheesy omelet, pepper jam mayo, maple syrup, and country gravy on a herb-buttered bun. It's breakfast, it's lunch, it's dinner...it is everything.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Modern Times Beer on July 29, 2021. May be an image of candle and drink.

node.text:
UPDATE: SOLD OUT 
—
MT8! To mark our 8th anniversary, our incredibly talented beverage conjurers summoned a lovely mélange of Riwaka, Nelson Sauvin, and Mosaic hops for this liquid celebration. This 8% DIPA is also beautifully complimented by a generous addition of @phantasm.nz powder (A.K.A. freeze-dried New Zealand Sauvignon Blanc grape dust), which make for a drinking experience akin to blowing out the birthday candles as a confetti cannon of fruit character explodes across the palate. You can totally snag cans at our spots.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Modern Times Beer on July 28, 2021 tagging @moderntimesdtla. May be an image of drink.

node.text: SPARKLE NECTAR! We took our hard-seltzer base and added insane quantities of mango and pineapple, then topped the whole thing off with coconut and vanilla. Yeah, pretty rad because the finished adult beverage is like a sparkling tropical smoothie. If you want in, cans will be up for grabs by the end of the week at all our spots, if they aren't already at your local MT hang.

buttons.text: Visit the COVID-19 Information Center for vaccine resources.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Modern Times Beer on July 28, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'MASH PLEASE BE EXCELLENT & RESPECT THE HEALTH & SAFETY OF YOUR FELLOW PARTYGOERS N'.

node.text: HEADS-UP, SD: We ask that all patrons wear a face covering while hanging at Lomaland, the Flavordome, & Far West Lounge, regardless of vaccination status. With Covid cases on the rise, we appreciate your patience & cooperation in keeping the tasting rooms safe, groovy places.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Modern Times Beer on July 27, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'MARKETING ASSISTANT SOCAL MARKETING COORDINATOR SAN DIEGO NOW HIRING APPLY AT MODERNTIMESBEER.COM/CAREERS Modern Times BEER'.

node.text: NOW HIRING: Marketing People. We are looking for a Marketing Coordinator and SoCal Marketing Assistant to join our team. If creating content is the name of your game and your organizational skills are second to none, we'd love to hear from you. All the details and apps are accessible via moderntimesbeer.com/careers.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Modern Times Beer on July 26, 2021. May be an image of indoor.

node.text: It's that ULTRA time of year again, which means our resident Prince of Prints is hard at work cranking out the insanely rad, screen printed labels that shall adorn the bottles of some of the most out-of-this-world liquid decadence in the known universe. Seriously, the time, effort, and supreme skill put into these beers is nothing short of magical, and we can't wait for the finished product.

node.text: POOL ZONE! We love a fully fledged, big bodied IPA as much as--if not significantly more than--the next guy, but sometimes, the fancy strikes for some lighter fare, especially in this heat. You can totally head to the special release presale page and get in on this 3.3% stunner right now.

node.text: WHAT IS SPARKLE NECTAR? That’s an excellent question, and we’re very glad you asked. We took a hard-seltzer base, then added massive quantities of mango and pineapple, and finally topped the whole thing off with coconut and vanilla. The result is a 5% adult beverage that’s like a sparkling tropical smoothie. We think it’s a pretty fantastic summer beverage, and we sincerely hope you agree. Cans are up for grabs in the online presale as we speak, if you want them.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Modern Times Beer on July 24, 2021. May be an image of drink.

node.text: Once again, we are asking you to check out a killer lineup of special release beers. For the second part of July's haul, we have some seriously kick-ass beverages, including a low cal IPA, rad revivals, ice cream-inspired luxuriousness, experimental caffeination, and lupulin-packed wonderment, plus our very first canned run of our smoothie-style seltzer. The presale is LIVE right now, and you can get there via the link in our profile.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Modern Times Beer on July 23, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text: SECRET BEACH BREAKDOWN! The coffees that comprise Secret Beach—showcased here both individually and in a pre-blended bag—are so good on their own that there’s a lot of room for very tasty experimentation. The Tanzania Iyenga offers a big-bodied bouquet of kiwi, strawberry, fruit punch, and nougat notes that are an amazing compliment to the Ethiopia Gedeb’s delicate, tea-like profile of pineapple, lime, and floral notes. These coffees are absolutely dynamite in concert, but they can be even more fun when you experiment with your own blends—hence, this opportunity for caffeinated creativity. These kits will be in the coming online special release presale, so keep your eyes peeled.

node.text:
CHECK IT OUT: We have the official guest brewery list for Nate Soroko's celebration of life. Friends and family will be getting together at our barrel warehouse on the 31st from 1PM-4PM to have some extremely choice beverages and toast to a truly extraordinary person. Tickets are available online now, and everyone who was lucky enough to know and love this industry icon is welcome to attend.
—
This event will benefit a local San Diego non-profit that provides culinary apprenticeships to people in need of a fresh start and a career.
